source.name: State Dropout and Completion Data
source.description: This Common Core of Data dataset reports the number of dropouts from each of grades 9 - 12 and the relevant event dropout rates and to report the numbers of high school diploma recipients, other high school completers, and the relevant Averaged Freshman Graduation Rate (AFGR).
